# 🛡️ SHE SHIELD – WOMEN SAFETY WEB APPLICATION

---

## 🚨 PROBLEM STATEMENT

Women face increasing safety concerns in public and private spaces.  
In emergency situations:

- Immediate help is not easily accessible  
- Sharing live location takes time  
- No quick one-click alert system  
- Delayed response increases risk  

There is a need for a fast, reliable, and easy-to-use digital safety solution.

---

## 💡 PROJECT DESCRIPTION

**She Shield** is a web-based Women Safety Application developed during a hackathon to provide instant emergency assistance.

The system enables users to send real-time SOS alerts, share live GPS location, and notify emergency contacts with a single click.

The main objective of this project is to reduce emergency response time and enhance women's safety using modern web technologies.

---

## 🔥 KEY FEATURES

- 🔴 One-Click Panic Button  
- 📍 Real-Time Location Tracking  
- 📩 Automatic SOS Alert to Emergency Contacts  
- 🗺️ Nearby Police Station & Hospital Finder  
- 🔐 Secure Login & Registration  
- 📱 Mobile Responsive Design  

---

## 🛠️ TECHNOLOGIES USED

### Frontend
