- SMS API  

---

## ⚙️ HOW IT WORKS

1. User registers and logs in.  
2. Adds trusted emergency contacts.  
3. Clicks the Panic Button during danger.  
4. System captures live location instantly.  
5. SOS alert message is sent to emergency contacts.  
6. Nearby police stations and hospitals are displayed.  

